⭐ What is a Star Schema? (Very Simple)
A Star Schema has:
•	1 Fact table (numbers / transactions)
•	Multiple Dimension tables (descriptions)
•	One-to-many relationships
•	Looks like a ⭐ star in Model View
✔ Faster reports
✔ Correct aggregations
✔ Easy DAX
________________________________________
